The former British No 1 was pictured sitting in an ice bath after a practice session and shared the picture on social media.

'No issues with ice baths when it's this hot in Florida,' Robson wrote on Facebook.

The latest social media update comes days after Robson spent time relaxing at country music festival Tortuga.

